    {
      "id": "658056d2-60ea-41aa-969e-b8fa4219cebd",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "It is possible to study regularly and still procrastinate, especially if the students waits until to late to increase the amount of studying. The authors examine the interactions of 674 student swith an eBook of introductory programming. ",
