    {
      "id": "f22dd393-1b0d-4fb1-bb9b-5dc72ac4fafd",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "When using SEM modelling, the authors find a small positive correlation between spacing and procrastination but, more importantly, find that there is a positive relationship between regular study intervals and final exam scores. No significant effect between procrastination and exam scores was found.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "f22dd393-1b0d-4fb1-bb9b-5dc72ac4fafd",
